    "constraints": [
      "Do not change the frozen schemas, HTTP contract, provider semantics, or persistence contract during the frontend refresh.",
      "Do not start P2 until all P0 and P1 work is green.",
      "Do not create cloud resources, publish a repository, deploy publicly, or submit without explicit human authorization.",
      "Never hide a failed LIVE call behind replay data."
